	<string>First Klick connects to your Bluetooth heart rate monitor to display live BPM during a run.</string>
	<key>NSBluetoothPeripheralUsageDescription</key>
	<string>First Klick connects to your Bluetooth heart rate monitor to display live BPM during a run.</string>
	<key>NSLocationAlwaysAndWhenInUseUsageDescription</key>
	<string>First Klick needs background location access to keep recording your run when the app is in the background.</string>
